## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c1d47-103">擴充辨別名稱的格式包含物件的 objectGUID 屬性的字串表示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1d47-103">The extended form of a distinguished name includes a string representation of the objectGUID property of an object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c1d47-104">例如使用者、 群組和電腦主體物件的安全性，擴充的表單也包含 [objectSID] 屬性的字串表示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1d47-104">For security principal objects such as users, groups, and computers, the extended form also includes a string representation of the objectSID property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c1d47-105">如需 objectGUID 和 objectSID 屬性的詳細資訊，請參閱[Object-guid](/windows/desktop/adschema/a-objectguid)並[物件 Sid](/windows/desktop/adschema/a-objectsid)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1d47-105">For more information about the objectGUID and objectSID properties, see [Object-Guid](/windows/desktop/adschema/a-objectguid) and [Object-Sid](/windows/desktop/adschema/a-objectsid).</span></span>
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c1d47-106">下列 C# 範例示範如何傳回十六進位格式的辨別名稱的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1d47-106">The following C# example shows how to return a collection of distinguished names in hexadecimal format.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.ExtendedDN = ExtendedDN.HexString;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```
